<!-- PROJECT INFO -->
<h2>📌 Project Overview</h2>

<p>
CloudSSO is a simulated enterprise-grade Single Sign-On system built using
Microsoft Entra ID authentication concepts and WordPress UI modules.
It demonstrates centralized authentication, employee management, and reporting.
</p>

<ul>
  <li>✔ Microsoft Entra ID Authentication</li>
  <li>✔ Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)</li>
  <li>✔ Employee Management System</li>
  <li>✔ Reporting &amp; Analytics Module</li>
  <li>✔ Cloud Integration (AWS / SQL Server concept)</li>
</ul>

<hr>

